These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
City: hamburg, san-francisco, edinburgh, hannover
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, soccer, skateboarding, weightlifting
There 4 different types of food: papaya, cranberry, lemon, banana
1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person eating papaya##1
4. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person eating lemon is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| City   | san-francisco    | hannover    | hamburg      | edinburgh    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | soccer | skateboarding | cricket |
| Food     | banana  | papaya       | cranberry    | lemon     |

