.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, turquise, ebony, chestnut
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, garlic, onion, cranberry
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, go, canasta
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
5. the person eating cranberry is between the owner of the frog and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the person playing canasta is between the person eating cranberry and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
9. the person eating onion is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | chestnut | turquise    | ebony  | coral    |
| Food   | artichoke      | garlic  | cranberry  | onion |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Game         | scrabble    | canasta | go | monopoly |

