.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, coral, aquamarine, amber
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, disco, classical
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, alhambra, vegafina, bongani
1. the fan of disco is the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is the person who likes amber##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes amber##2
9. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person eating lemon and the fan of hip-hop##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Color       | coral   | mauve   | aquamarine | amber |
| Music-Genre         | ambient   | disco | classical       | hip-hop    |
| Cigar   | vegafina    | alhambra | dunhill  | bongani    |

