.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, japanese, german
House: townhouse, palace, wooden, farmhouse
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, scooter, airplane
 1. the palace house is on the far right##1
 2. the farmhouse house is the mexican##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
 5. the farmhouse house is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the palace house is the japanese##1
 8. the townhouse house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 9. the mexican is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the malaysian is between the owner of the bird and the german##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Nationality           | mexican  | german | malaysian     | japanese |
| House   | farmhouse | townhouse  | wooden | palace       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Transport         | snowmobile | tram   | airplane   | scooter         |

