4 different games are played: poker, chess, whist, monopoly
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing chess##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person playing poker##2
10. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Flower          | azalea         | amaryllis         | balloon-flower     | begonia      |
| Birthday           | october | june | may    | april     |
