3. the polish is between the person watching epic movies and the dutch##2
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
8. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
9. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
