 2. the owner of the fish is the dutch##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the dutch and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the argentine is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
10. the dutch is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Pet   | rat | fish | dog  | goat  |
