The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, chef, dancer
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the architect is on the right of the chef##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the chef is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the dancer is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes orange##2
 9. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the designer##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Flower   | dahlia    | amaryllis    | lily      | aconite |
| Color       | blood-red        | ivory       | orange       | aquamarine     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Job        | designer       | dancer     | chef         | architect           |

