 3. the photographer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the journalist##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the hamster##2
 6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking sprite is the pilot##1
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is the cape-cod house##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job        | journalist  | pilot | photographer     | designer     |
| Pet         | hamster | goldfish | goat     | guinea-pig |
| Beverage       | fanta  | sprite   | hot-chocolate | tea    |
| House   | cape-cod   | colonial   | ranch-style  | gothic-revival        |

